org.opendaylight.controller.config.manager.impl.dependencyresolver

Class DependencyResolverManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.config.manager.impl.dependencyresolver.DependencyResolverManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, DependencyResolverFactory

    public class DependencyResolverManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements DependencyResolverFactory, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    Holds information about modules being created and destroyed within this transaction. Observes usage of DependencyResolver within modules to figure out dependency tree.
